### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Register a new user
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "sachin",
  "email": "sachin@gmail.com",
  "password": "securepassword123"
}

### 2. Login (This will return the token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "sachin@gmail.com",
  "password": "securepassword123"
}

### 3. Get all people (Protected)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/people
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Match a face embedding (Protected)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/people/match
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "embedding": [0.12, -0.45, 0.88, 0.01, -0.3]
}

### 5. Get a specific person by ID (Protected)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/people/PERSON_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
